snippet.title: Manitoba Crime Stoppers  - Amber McFarland
snippet.description:
**There is a $20,000 reward for info leading to Ambers' location**

Amber McFarland is 24 years-old, she was last seen on Friday Oct. 18/08 at a bar in Portage La Prairie. Friends say the following morning her car was found in exactly the same place she'd left it.

Amber hasn't been seen or heard from since. Friends say it's unlike her to not show up, which is exactly what happened at her place of work. She was due for a shift at Marks Work Wearhouse on Saturday morning.
Amber has blonde hair, green eyes, stands about 5'6"-5'7", and weighs 135 lbs. She was wearing a black sweater and blue jeans when she went missing.

Please help us! Be aware! Be vigilant! Amber is still out there and we must bring her home!

Amber is a deeply loved SISTER, a greatly missed DAUGHTER, a loving AUNTIE and a great FRIEND. Help us bring her home!

SOMEONE KNOWS WHERE AMBER IS,,,

Crime Stoppers pays cash for information on any unsolved crime.

Winnipeg Crime Stoppers @ 786-8477
Manitoba Crime Stoppers @ 1-800-222-8477

Callers never have to reveal their identity

Please call with information RCMP in Portage @ 204-857-4445
